CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 21, 1959, pg. A12, reads: "CELEBRATE WEDDING ANNIVERSARY - Mr. and Mrs. Reese Mosley, center, celebrated their 30th wedding anniversary with relatives and friends at their home. With them are, left, Dorothy and Frank Prime, and right, Beatrice Clayton and Mrs. Susan Jenkins.  Other guests were the William Owenses, the Ray McPhersons, the Fred Lockharts, the Louis Cooks, the Robert Hawkinses, the Robert Eldridges, the James Moyers, Mmes. Florence Benett, Charlotte Johnson, Margaret Woodley, George Meads, Crystal Clinton, Miss Sudie Williams, Ted Owens and Edward Smith. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Reese Mosley wearing striped tie, and Mrs. Mosley wearing corsage, standing behind cake on their 30th wedding anniversary, with Dorothy and Frank Prime on left, and Beatrice Clayton and Susan Jenkins on right, in home, another version
